class ListNode:
    def __init__(self, val=0, next=None):
        self.val = val
        self.next = next

def addTwoNumbers(l1, l2):
    def list_to_linked(arr):
        if not arr: return None
        head = ListNode(arr[0])
        curr = head
        for val in arr[1:]:
            curr.next = ListNode(val)
            curr = curr.next
        return head
    
    l1 = list_to_linked(l1)
    l2 = list_to_linked(l2)
    
    dummy = ListNode(0)
    curr = dummy
    carry = 0
    
    while l1 or l2 or carry:
        val1 = l1.val if l1 else 0
        val2 = l2.val if l2 else 0
        total = val1 + val2 + carry
        
        carry = total // 10
        curr.next = ListNode(total % 10)
        curr = curr.next
        
        if l1: l1 = l1.next
        if l2: l2 = l2.next
    
    result = []
    curr = dummy.next
    while curr:
        result.append(curr.val)
        curr = curr.next
    return result
